  "title": "Business Development Director",
  "description": "<p>Primary Responsibilities:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>1. Responsible for identifying new business opportunities and new markets for the company to expand into.</p>\n<p>2. Responsible for the development of company expansion plans.</p>\n<p>3. Responsible for maximizing the business opportunities within the defined sales territory</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job functions:</p>\n<p>1. To implement all aspects of sales related activities such as planning, monitoring and measuring of customers within the defined territory</p>\n<p>2. Strong interpersonal communication skills</p>\n<p>3. Strong analytical skills - Ability to recognise trends and patterns in the market in order to identify potential new business opportunities</p>\n<p>4.  To keep in touch with market regarding on competitive pricing, promotion, products, etc</p>\n<p>5. Building long-term relationships with new and existing customers</p>\n<p>6. To develop staff into service professionals and groom high potentials to leadership roles.</p>\n<p>7. To Perform advanced hair cutting and hair coloring such as highlights, ombre, and balayage.</p>\n<p>8. Styles hair, including blowouts, curls, braids, ponytails, and updos.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Jober Pte Ltd UEN 201616711G</p>\n<p>EA License No: 16C8401</p>\n<p>XING CHONG | Registration No: R22109860</p>\n<p>#SGUnitedJobs</p>\n<p>Website : https://www.jobersg.com/</p>",
